title: Make Tiny Adjustments
itunes:title: Make Tiny Adjustments
description:
Episode 291 -  You are so much closer to success than you realize and you do not need massive adjustments to have a completely different life. Usually, it is a series of small adjustments that change the outcome of your life and your success.
